    "description": "Jelly Beans Group Co., Ltd. plans, develops, wholesales, and retails non-leather women's footwear in Japan. The company offers its products primarily under the JELLY BEANS brand. It also imports and exports women's shoes. In addition, the company provides designing consulting, supply chain, and after-sales services. It sells its products to department stores and shopping malls. Further, it engages in the distribution of food products. Additionally, it engages in the freight forwarding; warehousing and warehouse management; rail transport; marine transport; air transport; and logistics consulting business. The company also operates online shops. The company was formerly known as Amagasa Co., Ltd. and changed its name to JELLY BEANS GROUP Co., Ltd. in September 2024. Jelly Beans Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
